Written progeny_pathway_activity.csv + progeny_pathway_sign_prior.csv to results/real_signedLRBase 

Note: PROGENy's model is PRE-BUILT, so steps (1)+(2) run on ANY human
dataset unchanged -- no per-dataset marker curation. Only step (3),
activity->sign, keeps a thin irreducible prior.
